                    联系我们: xxxxxxxxxxxx@foxmail.com
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #747474;">
                    This is an automated email, please do not reply.<br>
                    © Dialogue
                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>
</body>
</html>